headline: TD Cowen Remains a Hold on Fiserv (FISV)
summary: ​Fiserv, Inc. (NASDAQ:FISV) is one of the Most Undervalued Fintech Stocks to Buy Now. On January 12, Bryan Bergin from TD Cowen reiterated a Hold rating on the stock and lowered the firm’s price target from $80 to $77.
